\PhpCollection

Namespaces

ObjectBasicsHandler
Tests

Traits

EntityLikeObject Implementation for ObjectBasics for entity-like objects.

Interfaces

CollectionInterface Basic interface which adds some behaviors, and a few methods common to all collections.
MapInterface Basic map interface.
ObjectBasics Interface that must be implemented by objects that are used as keys, or in sets.
ObjectBasicsHandler Interface for external handlers that provide ObjectBasics functionality.
SequenceInterface Interface for mutable sequences.
SetInterface Interface for sets.
SortableInterface Interface for sortable collections.

Classes

AbstractCollection
AbstractMap A simple map implementation which basically wraps an array with an object oriented interface.
AbstractSequence A sequence with numerically indexed elements.
Map A simple map implementation which basically wraps an array with an object oriented interface.
ObjectBasicsHandlerRegistry Registry for handlers that provide ObjectBasics functionality for classes.
Sequence Unsorted sequence implementation.
Set Implementation of a Set.
SortedSequence A sequence with a fixed sort-order.
